Style

style 
- for styling HTML element
- format: <tagname style="cssproperty:cssvalue;"></tagname>

css properties include:
background-color for background color
color for text colors
font-family for text fonts
font-size for text sizes
text-align for text alignment

style in p
<p style="color:#e8d7c9; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; font-size: 14pt;">Hello, I'm Vanessa! Welcome to my first web portfolio!</p>

CSS
Cascading Style Sheets used to beautify the website

Added to HTML Doc in 3 ways:
Inline
Internal 
External

